In this case, the sliding window of formula_80 across the past formula_47 units of time is best approximated by a linear combination of the first formula_82 shifted Legendre polynomials, weighted together by the elements of formula_83 at time formula_29:
formula_85

When combined with deep learning methods, these networks can be trained to outperform long short-term memory units and related architectures, while using fewer computational resources.

